BattleTanks is a head-to-head tank combat game in a specific terrain with obstacles. Obstacles can be used for advantage.

RULES
- Terrain will be surrounded by mountains. Tanks can move anywhere between these mountains.
- Players will start with finite health and ammunition.
- Each hit taken reduces health. (Direct or indirect)
- The last player standing wins.

REQUIREMENTS
- SFX : Gun fire, explosion, barrel or turret moving, engine sound
- Static mesh : Simple tank body parts, turret, barrel, wheels
- Music : Background music
